{"tid":1543870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"譴責何君堯干擾學校 還校園寧靜","createTime":"2019-09-05T10:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T17:44:42.000Z","uid":106672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"625ceaf278835b4e6a652885c56b57f30e4c6e09","tid":1543870,"uid":106672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"繼上星期立法會議員何君堯去信本校，要求校長交待有否支持同學罷課活動後，連日來皆有同一群不知名人士於本校附近徘徊。該等人士時而查問本校上課情況，時而裝作購買門票，時而於門外徘徊，不但對本校正常運作造成嚴重干擾，更威脅到本校老師及學生之人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n本校強調，黑色上衣乃本校學生校服其中一款，而學生穿著校服回校上課乃天公地道。<br />\n而今日何君堯更在不理解本校運作的情況下，於記者會中抹黑書院運作。我們對此等惡劣行徑予以強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n香港兆基創意書院致力為香港培育文化藝術人才，老師堅守專業，我們重視同學的自主學習及安全。一間學校如何運作，書院一直有跟教育局保持溝通，我們不認為我們需要回應個別議員的言論。<br />\n<br />\n為了維護本校良好、包容及寧靜的學習環境，以及保護學生人身安全，何議員應立即停止有關無理行為，令社會政治爭論止步於校園外。<br />\n<br />\n香港兆基創意書院<br />\n2019年9月5日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70631321_2236767659785059_3844724057589153792_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQmgGX2dELArdpIAjO6t2v6PH-LsmYnzRiYpY6mO3Q1ft4Nw6vvdlXvjq0paNLkFxAY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=c76a81ae7e5df68394cc0e4b036b6557&amp;oe=5DCBF081\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F70631321_2236767659785059_3844724057589153792_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQmgGX2dELArdpIAjO6t2v6PH-LsmYnzRiYpY6mO3Q1ft4Nw6vvdlXvjq0paNLkFxAY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3Dc76a81ae7e5df68394cc0e4b036b6557%26oe%3D5DCBF081&h=908e5929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9976c1071b7be3199ad70eff5079c81d8d2c1818","tid":1543870,"uid":173058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">9月遊行重頭炮</span></span>！到時一齊揮美國旗同唱美國國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啲練定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtJenXB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtJenXB.jpg&h=ce58872f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYqkivV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYqkivV.jpg&h=12e153dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.soundcloud.com/iahc/usa-national-anthem-star-spangled-banner\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundcloud.com%2Fiahc%2Fusa-national-anthem-star-spangled-banner&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=88dc8de7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundcloud.com/iahc/usa-national-anthem-star-spangled-banner</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K88Rqbo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK88Rqbo.png&h=2bfa9f14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLgLuC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLgLuC4.jpg&h=6a256396&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54d0a72dc87d1550ae52a08975e6e3848d2233db","tid":1543870,"uid":269649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:00:55.000Z","msg":"推爆，支持教學自由，鄙視畜生議員，粗暴干涉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e4178cf609be18fac9ea6a4e294e81f2fbb1b4","tid":1543870,"uid":302165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"何君堯老婆補習社招生<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/reNoPSVqzFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FreNoPSVqzFc&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=a6f0f1f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/reNoPSVqzF